title: Thanksgiving NFL Game Picks (Football 11/21)
description:
Will Brinson is joined by CBS Sports NFL Insider Jason La Canfora to make picks for the Thanksgiving games including the Bears-Lions (8:00), Redskins-Cowboys (15:00) with an appearance by the one and only Copper La Canfora and Falcons-Saints (26:20). They also break down the insanity of the Chiefs-Rams game (35:15) and Lamar Jackson's debut (45:45).
